From: SJ Park <sj@kernel.org>
Date: Sun, 28 Jun 2026 10:50:39 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] ==== attrs only monitoring ====

mm/damon: introduce data attributes only monitoring

DAMON monitors data attributes (probe_hits) in addition to data access
information.  Still, data access is the primary information that DAMON
is providing.  Regions are adjusted for accurate access information.  In
some cases, users may interested in data attributes more than data
access information.

Introduce data attributes only monitoring.

Signed-off-by: SJ Park <sj@kernel.org>
